title: California vaccine law: Opponents' repeal effort fails, but fight goes on
text:
08 California vaccine law: Opponents' repeal effort fails, but fight goes on 
San Jose Mercury News: The fight to repeal California's controversial new mandatory vaccine law officially ended this week before it even got to the ballot box, as opponents on Wednesday conceded an ill-fated petition drive fell woefully short on signatures.
